<h1>Privacy Policy (EN) — BetBrain</h1>
<p class="muted"><b>Effective Date:</b> [DD Month YYYY] <br>
<b>Publisher:</b> HawksAppStudio <br>
<b>Support:</b> hawksappstudio@gmail.com</p>

<h2>1) Overview</h2>
<p>This Privacy Policy explains how we collect, use, and share information when you use the App.</p>

<h2>2) Information We Collect</h2>
<p>Depending on your usage and enabled features, we may collect:</p>
<ul>
  <li><b>Purchase & Subscription Data</b>: subscription status and entitlements processed via RevenueCat.</li>
  <li><b>Analytics, Performance & Crash Data</b>: app events, device info, app version, crash logs via Firebase.</li>
  <li><b>Advertising Data</b>: ad impressions/clicks and related measurement via Google AdMob.</li>
  <li><b>Support Communications</b>: information you provide when contacting support.</li>
</ul>
<div class="box">
  <p><b>Note:</b> We do not intentionally collect sensitive personal data (e.g., health data) and do not knowingly collect data from children.</p>
</div>

<h2>3) How We Use Information</h2>
<ul>
  <li>Operate and improve the App</li>
  <li>Deliver subscription entitlements and access</li>
  <li>Display and measure ads (if applicable)</li>
  <li>Fix bugs, prevent fraud/abuse, and improve performance</li>
  <li>Respond to support requests</li>
</ul>

<h2>4) Sharing of Information</h2>
<p>We may share data with service providers used to run the App, including RevenueCat (subscriptions), Firebase (analytics/crash), and Google AdMob (ads/measurement), and with authorities if required by law.</p>

<h2>5) Data Retention</h2>
<p>We retain information only as long as needed for the purposes described, then delete or anonymize it unless legal obligations require longer retention.</p>

<h2>6) Your Choices & Rights</h2>
<p>Depending on your location, you may have rights to access, correct, delete, or restrict processing of your data. You can manage ad personalization through device settings (where available). For requests, contact <b>hawksappstudio@gmail.com</b>.</p>

<h2>7) Security</h2>
<p>We use reasonable safeguards to protect information. No method of transmission or storage is 100% secure.</p>

<h2>8) International Transfers</h2>
<p>Your data may be processed in countries other than your own via our service providers. We use safeguards where required by law.</p>

<h2>9) Changes</h2>
<p>We may update this Policy. We will publish the updated version with a new effective date.</p>

<h2>10) Contact</h2>
<p>Privacy questions: <b>hawksappstudio@gmail.com</b></p>

